title: 224: The Murder of Jessica Chambers: An ID Mystery
itunes:title: The Murder of Jessica Chambers: An ID Mystery
description:
On December 6, 2014, 19-year-old Jessica Chambers was set on fire and left for dead. Her injuries were horrific and she died a few hours later. Who would do this to the popular young woman, and why? Investigators had few clues to go as the dogged search for Jessica's killer takes over her small town.
